c-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/mach-ban-5-phan-mem-ghep-anh-don-gian-mien-phi.html\/#Phan_mem_ghep_anh_-_Fotor\" title=\"Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m gh\u00e9p \u1ea3nh &#8211; Fotor\">Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m gh\u00e9p \u1ea3nh &#8211; Fotor<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/mach-ban-5-phan-mem-ghep-anh-don-gian-mien-phi.html\/#Picasa\" title=\"Picasa\">Picasa<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/mach-ban-5-phan-mem-ghep-anh-don-gian-mien-phi.html\/#Instagram_Layout_Layout_from_Instagram\" title=\"Instagram Layout\/ Layout from Instagram\">Instagram Layout\/ Layout from Instagram<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/mach-ban-5-phan-mem-ghep-anh-don-gian-mien-phi.html\/#Phan_mem_ghep_anh_don_gian_-_Photo_Collage\" title=\"Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m gh\u00e9p \u1ea3nh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n &#8211; Photo Collage\">Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m gh\u00e9p \u1ea3nh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n &#8211; Photo Collage<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/mach-ban-5-phan-mem-ghep-anh-don-gian-mien-phi.html\/#Ribbet\" title=\"Ribbet\">Ribbet<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/mach-ban-5-phan-mem-ghep-anh-don-gian-mien-phi.html\/#Tong_ket\" title=\"T\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft\">T\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong>Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m gh\u00e9p \u1ea3nh<\/strong> cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gh\u00e9p c\u00e1c b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh kh\u00e1c nhau th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh duy nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gh\u00e9p \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p, v\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 Photoshop ho\u1eb7c PhotoScape&#8230;D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 <strong>5 ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m gh\u00e9p \u1ea3nh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/strong> b\u1ea1n n\u00ean t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u.<\/p>\n<p>C\u00f9ng theo ch\u00e2n <strong>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/strong> t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u ngay th\u00f4i n\u00e0o!!!<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Phan_mem_ghep_anh_-_Fotor\"><\/span><strong>Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m gh\u00e9p \u1ea3nh &#8211; Fotor<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>N\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3: Web, Android, iOS, Windows Phone<\/p>\n<p><strong>Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m gh\u00e9p \u1ea3nh Fotor<\/strong> h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gh\u00e9p \u1ea3nh v\u00e0o khung v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu \u0111\u1eb9p. \u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb PC t\u1edbi di \u0111\u1ed9ng. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u01b0u \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng \u1ea3nh ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8990\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/top-5-phan-mem-ghep-anh-mien-phi-va-tot-nhat-cho-may-tinh-300x203.jpg\" alt=\"phan mem ghep anh\" width=\"700\" height=\"473\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/top-5-phan-mem-ghep-anh-mien-phi-va-tot-nhat-cho-may-tinh-300x203.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/top-5-phan-mem-ghep-anh-mien-phi-va-tot-nhat-cho-may-tinh-768x518.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/top-5-phan-mem-ghep-anh-mien-phi-va-tot-nhat-cho-may-tinh.jpg 920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Fotor, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eaft, d\u00e1n \u1ea3nh ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt, th\u00eam hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng, template \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng t\u00ednh sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Fotor c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 ch\u1ec9nh \u1ea3nh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd nh\u01b0 xoay, l\u1eadt h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e1ng,\u2026<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Picasa\"><\/span><strong>Picasa<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>N\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3:\u00a0Mac, Windows, Chrome App<\/p>\n<p>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u00ean phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n n\u1ec1n web nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n d\u00e0nh cho PC.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8992\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/3-phan-mem-chinh-sua-anh-tieng-viet-tot-nhat-1-300x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/3-phan-mem-chinh-sua-anh-tieng-viet-tot-nhat-1-300x150.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/3-phan-mem-chinh-sua-anh-tieng-viet-tot-nhat-1.jpg 710w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng xem \u1ea3nh, ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda \u1ea3nh, ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh c\u00f2n tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00ean trang Web c\u1ee7a Google \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng chia s\u1ebb cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n b\u00e8.<\/p>\n<p><strong><em>Xem th\u00eam:<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/phan-mem-ghep-audio-vao-video.html\/\">Gh\u00e9p audio v\u00e0o video d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/phan-mem-noi-video-don-gian.html\/\">Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m n\u1ed1i video \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t<\/a><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8993\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/phan-mem-xem-anh-picasa-4-300x216.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"504\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/phan-mem-xem-anh-picasa-4-300x216.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/phan-mem-xem-anh-picasa-4-768x553.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/phan-mem-xem-anh-picasa-4.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng cho ph\u00e9p ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem \u1ea3nh d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng thumbnail ho\u1eb7c full m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00f9y \u00fd ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh g\u1ed3m m\u00e0u s\u1eafc, \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e1ng,\u2026m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Instagram_Layout_Layout_from_Instagram\"><\/span><strong>Instagram Layout\/ Layout from Instagram<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>N\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3: iOS, Android<\/p>\n<p><strong>Instagram Layout<\/strong> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1o khung c\u1ee7a Instagram. \u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o, c\u1eaft d\u00e1n v\u00e0 chia s\u1ebb \u1ea3nh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i nhanh, g\u1ecdn, nh\u1eb9 h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8994\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/3042427_Screen_Shot_2015-05-20_at_07.21.52-300x255.jpg\" alt=\"phan mem ghep anh\" width=\"700\" height=\"596\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/3042427_Screen_Shot_2015-05-20_at_07.21.52-300x255.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/3042427_Screen_Shot_2015-05-20_at_07.21.52-1024x871.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/3042427_Screen_Shot_2015-05-20_at_07.21.52-768x653.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/3042427_Screen_Shot_2015-05-20_at_07.21.52.jpg 1394w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Giao di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Instagram Layout kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 g\u1ecdn nh\u1eb9. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch k\u00e9o, th\u1ea3. Khi \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t, b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 vi\u1ec7c l\u01b0u v\u00e0 chia s\u1ebb \u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p t\u1edbi b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Phan_mem_ghep_anh_don_gian_-_Photo_Collage\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 23.04px;\"><b>Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m gh\u00e9p \u1ea3nh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n &#8211; Photo Collage<\/b><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>N\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3: Web<\/p>\n<p><em><strong>Xem th\u00eam:<\/strong><\/em>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/phan-mem-tao-clip-chuyen-nghiep.html\/\">T\u1ed5ng H\u1ee3p Top 6 Ph\u1ea7n M\u1ec1m L\u00e0m Clip Chuy\u00ean Nghi\u1ec7p Tr\u00ean M\u00e1y T\u00ednh<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n t\u1ed1n ti\u1ec1n cho c\u00e1c ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m \u0111\u1eaft ti\u1ec1n. Photo Collage, b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng c\u0103n b\u1ea3n.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8995\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/photo-collage-max-300x195.jpg\" alt=\"phan mem ghep a nh don gian mien phi\" width=\"700\" height=\"455\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/photo-collage-max-300x195.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/photo-collage-max.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 web n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c h\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh t\u1eeb PC t\u1edbi di \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 Mac OS X, Windows, iOS v\u00e0 Android.<\/p>\n<p>Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n k\u00e9o\/th\u1ea3, upload \u1ea3nh l\u00ean trang web. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00f9y \u00fd ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ch\u00e8n template, th\u00eam ch\u1eef, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. Photo Collage h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u01b0u v\u1ec1 d\u01b0\u1edbi 4 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng JPG, PNG, PDF v\u00e0 BMP.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ribbet\"><\/span><strong>Ribbet<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>N\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3: Web, Chrome App<\/p>\n<p>B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u m\u1ed9t trang web ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda \u1ea3nh mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p nh\u01b0 Ribbet hi\u1ec7n nay. V\u1edbi Ribbet, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eeda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ch\u1ec9 trong m\u1ed9t c\u00fa nh\u1ea5p chu\u1ed9t, crop, thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea3nh d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8996\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/bhgvfcfj-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"phan mem ghep anh\" widt